<HEADLINE> Ordenstein Avoids Prison Time </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ALBUQUERQUE (AP) -- Former New Mexico football player Kawika  
Ordenstein, who pleaded no contest to beating up a Lobos track 
athlete last year, avoided prison time in a sentence handed down 
Tuesday. 
</P>
