85,000 were expected. 
</P>
<P>
	Before the final in Pasadena, Norway plays Brazil in the  
third-place game. 
</P>
<P>
	The crowd expected Saturday would be a record for a women's  
sporting event, Marla Messing, president of the organizing 
committee, said. The current record is 78,972 for a World Cup 
doubleheader at Giants Stadium on June 19. 
  	   	
